data.description: Excellent Reserve at Sonoma Verde luxury home!     Awesome hill country sunset views from your back patio. Spacious and welcoming; this custom-built, home features an open feel and great natural light.     Perfect for in-door & out-door entertaining with a spacious chef's kitchen.     Meticulously maintained and detailed, this home provides excellent access to San Antonio and points west into the Texas hill country.
